    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wipe the reserved pan clean and return it to a medium heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, crack your <strong>eggs</strong> into the pan</p><p>Cover with a lid and cook for 2-3 min or until done to your liking</p>",
