      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>jacket potatoes</strong> topped with a <strong>fried egg</strong>, then season with a small pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>prosciutto croque madame jacket potato</strong></p><p>Serve the<strong> dressed salad </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
